 not desired.

Package: gemian-desktop-minimal
Architecture: any
Depends: ${germinate:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: ${germinate:Recommends}
Description: Gemian minimal desktop system
 This package depends on the core set for a functional Gemian system
 .
 It is safe to remove this package if some of the included packages are
 not desired.
